    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is exactly how my Norwegian grandmother made berry jam, and in truth, its how I prefer it. <br />No quite jam but just as nice is fresh white bread smeared with butter, topped with sliced, sweet strawberries and sugar sprinkled on top&#8230;.fold in half or roll up and have a napkin ready to mop up any juices.  Yum.  <br />Queensland strawberries are hitting the shelves with abandon in Australia now so this might well be my weekend project &#8211; thanks for posting!</p>
    </div>

