      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/07/you-dont-forget/#comment-29949"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-07-30T07:58:31-04:00">Saturday, July 30, 2011 at 7:58 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is a great recipe. We grow strawberries in buckets at the back of garden in a sunny corner. However, we added a few extra ingredients. In one batch we added cracked black pepper and in the other we added chili (also home grown) and lime. The chili and lime batch went really well with a strong cheddar.</p>
    </div>

