      <p>Hello! <br />So I made this recipe and it was awesome! Really elevated the flavor of some already amazing strawberries. 🙂<br />A funny thing happened though; I put the berries in an jar to store and screwed the lid on it while the mixture was still hot and it actually sealed! Do you think I could store the berries at room temp if I had sanitized the jar first? I would love to make a large batch of this now to have for the winter. 🙂</p>
