    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Pensione Nichols, one block above the Market, is reasonable and charming.</p>
<p>The Hoods are done in Portland, have been for awhile, and I am a strawberry snob about Hoods.  But the Seascapes aren&#39;t bad and you can still get them here, and it&#39;s the first week of August.  I say go for it.</p>
    </div>

